1
00:00:15,900 --> 00:00:16,780
Take a look for yourself.

2
00:00:17,499 --> 00:00:18,580
What have you done?

3
00:00:18,819 --> 00:00:20,139
This is how you treat clients?

4
00:00:26,940 --> 00:00:28,540
Be careful, don't break it.

5
00:00:38,020 --> 00:00:40,139
Madam, I've finished cleaning.

6
00:00:40,259 --> 00:00:41,060
The pool.

7
00:00:43,859 --> 00:00:44,579
Okay.

8
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:46,139
You're not fooling the client,

9
00:00:46,300 --> 00:00:47,579
you're fooling yourself.

10
00:00:47,579 --> 00:00:48,660
Take it back and redo it.

11
00:01:35,379 --> 00:01:35,900
Madam,

12
00:01:36,499 --> 00:01:37,420
where's my necklace?

13
00:01:38,299 --> 00:01:39,379
What necklace?

14
00:01:39,820 --> 00:01:41,540
You just finished cleaning my room,

15
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:43,019
and now my necklace is missing.

16
00:01:47,499 --> 00:01:49,620
Madam, there's no need for this.

17
00:01:51,139 --> 00:01:53,060
If you don't like me, I can leave.

18
00:01:54,139 --> 00:01:56,620
But framing me like this...

19
00:01:56,620 --> 00:01:57,700
It's really...

20
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:59,379
If you're innocent,

21
00:01:59,540 --> 00:02:00,780
it'll come out in the search.

22
00:02:04,299 --> 00:02:05,060
Besides,

23
00:02:05,499 --> 00:02:06,900
I don't want to drive you away.

24
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:09,060
Who do you think you are?

25
00:02:09,060 --> 00:02:09,780
Madam,

26
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:12,539
I'm here because of Young Master Jing.

27
00:02:13,499 --> 00:02:14,819
You treat me like this,

28
00:02:15,180 --> 00:02:16,900
don't you afraid he'll be unhappy?

29
00:02:17,659 --> 00:02:19,419
I just want him to be unhappy.

30
00:02:19,659 --> 00:02:20,460
So what?

31
00:02:26,140 --> 00:02:27,539
We are both women,

32
00:02:28,499 --> 00:02:29,900
and this is all you've got?

33
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:34,060
How did you even marry into the Gu family?

34
00:02:36,259 --> 00:02:37,900
Do you really want to marry into the Gu family?

35
00:02:39,699 --> 00:02:41,300
Whether I can marry into the Gu family

36
00:02:41,659 --> 00:02:43,539
depends on your help.

37
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:46,099
Madam, I couldn't find it.

38
00:02:49,659 --> 00:02:51,780
Madam, I really didn't steal it.

39
00:02:51,780 --> 00:02:53,219
I didn't take your necklace.

40
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:54,860
When I was tidying up for you today,

41
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:56,020
I didn't see it.

42
00:02:56,659 --> 00:02:58,620
Madam, it wasn't me, I swear.

43
00:03:15,499 --> 00:03:16,219
Xiaoxue.

44
00:03:18,860 --> 00:03:19,620
Ji Xiaoxue.

45
00:03:25,140 --> 00:03:25,819
Xiaoxue.

46
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:53,620
Ji Xiaoxue.

47
00:03:55,020 --> 00:03:56,539
What are you doing here? Who told you to do this?

48
00:03:57,020 --> 00:03:58,259
Madam told me to do it.

49
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:02,740
Come, follow me.

50
00:04:03,020 --> 00:04:03,819
No.

51
00:04:04,860 --> 00:04:05,699
Madam said

52
00:04:05,939 --> 00:04:07,379
I can't leave until I finish today's work.

53
00:04:09,539 --> 00:04:10,659
I told you not to do it.

54
00:04:11,659 --> 00:04:13,060
This is not your job.

55
00:04:13,780 --> 00:04:14,380
Let's go.

56
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:18,700
When I was cleaning the room for her today,

57
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:20,140
her necklace was missing.

58
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:21,940
She said I did it.

59
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,179
But I really didn't take it.

60
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:26,940
She said if I don't finish these,

61
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:29,460
she did it on purpose.

62
00:04:36,099 --> 00:04:36,859
Let's go.

63
00:04:39,979 --> 00:04:40,659
What happened?

64
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:44,219
I sprained my ankle

65
00:04:44,419 --> 00:04:45,859
cleaning the pool today.

66
00:04:47,099 --> 00:04:48,059
How are you feeling now?

67
00:04:49,059 --> 00:04:49,780
It hurts.

68
00:04:52,059 --> 00:04:52,700
Come on,

69
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:36,940
I'll get you some medicine.

70
00:06:38,859 --> 00:06:39,780
Don't go.

71
00:06:42,539 --> 00:06:43,780
I failed to protect you.

72
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:47,020
I'm fine.

73
00:06:48,099 --> 00:06:50,299
I don't want you to have conflicts with them because of me.

74
00:06:50,299 --> 00:06:51,020
No way.

75
00:06:51,859 --> 00:06:52,940
No one can bully you.

76
00:08:08,340 --> 00:08:09,260
Where's Ji Xiaoxue?

77
00:08:12,580 --> 00:08:14,580
She's my personal assistant now.

78
00:08:15,260 --> 00:08:16,539
She doesn't have to do these things anymore.

79
00:08:18,859 --> 00:08:20,099
In that case,

80
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:22,700
Ji Xiaoxue can't live in our Gu family.

81
00:08:24,539 --> 00:08:25,539
In our Gu family,

82
00:08:27,739 --> 00:08:28,940
I still have some say, right?
